43.3 亚组分析
使用jstable，只要1行代码即可！！！

library(jstable)

res &lt;- TableSubgroupMultiCox(

  # 指定公式
  formula = Surv(time, status) ~ rx, 

  # 指定哪些变量有亚组
  var_subgroups = c("sex","age","obstruct","perfor","adhere",
                    "differ","extent","surg","node4"), 
  data = df #指定你的数据
  )
